Roll No  | Hindi | English |  Computer
  1      |  86   |         |
  2      |       |    78   | 
  3      |  69   |         |   78

NoSql
> Not a sql
> JSON
> Both structred and unstructred
> Nested Data

[
    {
        "rollNo":1,
